steps.name: Click on 'New Item' in the side menu
Click 'Save' button on the BaseConfigPage page
Click on the 'Configure' button on side menu
Click on the 'Configure' Button on the Base Job Page
Select Choice Parameter from drop-down menu
Input boolean parameter Choice parameter name test
Input [choice one, choice two, choice three] as parameter choices
Input Choice parameter desc test as parameter description
Click 'Save' button on the BaseConfigPage page
Click on a build with parameters
